## Large Files

If a task produces large files (images, PDFs, etc.):
- Do NOT commit binary files larger than 1MB to git
- Instead, note the file path in your task output so the GM can upload it separately

## Output Format

When you complete a task:
1. Commit all work to the task branch
2. Write a brief summary of what you did as your final message
3. Include any file paths, URLs, or assets the GM needs for delivery

